Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:55.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}携手 松手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:56.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无论几次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}和你 和你
