Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:03.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不会再次分离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:04.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}sha-la-la♪
